text: Camilla Gunell (born September 7, 1970) is a politician within the Åland Islands, an autonomous and unilingually Swedish territory of Finland, and the former Premier of the Government of Åland. ==Positions== ===Current=== ===Past=== *Member of the lagting (The Parliament of Åland) 2007–2011 *Minister of Education and Culture 2005–2007 *Member of the lagting (The Parliament of Åland) 2003–2005Camilla Gunell , page at Ålands landskapsregering.
